  "title": "BiomeBloom",
  "description": "Transforms sky, fog, and water colors across every biome for a richer, more atmospheric Minecraft experience.",
  "body": "<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/polytone\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1263505236845269032/1447927480638902312/295781845-7c5bb84a-5aa8-4883-9e23-c27e8ce60c22.png?ex=6939670c&is=6938158c&hm=1e4bed2fdea5681eb0badfb1d9d98536d4eb8f0fe0779fdad8a514dc760458b8&\"\n         width=\"450\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n---\n\n# 🌄 **BiomeBloom**\n\n**BiomeBloom** transforms your Minecraft world through dynamic **sky, fog, and water color variations** based on each biome.  \nEvery region gains its own mood — from bright tropical waters to misty forests and crisp, icy tundras with pale horizons.\n\n---\n\n## ✨ Features\n\n- Biome-specific **sky color** variations  \n- Immersive **fog gradients** unique to each region  \n- Distinct **water tints** for oceans, rivers & swamps  \n\n---\n\n<p align=\"center\"><i>Every sky tells a new story.</i></p>\n\n---\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/C0C2154WDY\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1263505236845269032/1447933978857312338/support_me_on_kofi_red.png?ex=69396d19&is=69381b99&hm=7757f4e557f288b1abf410f22a2db0bbcfedb6771c4316252edf4668469cc78f&\"\n         width=\"250\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n",
